Class CampParticipantDatabase

java.lang.Object
database.Database
database.CampParticipantDatabase
All Implemented Interfaces:
iDatabase
public class CampParticipantDatabase extends Database
Database class for handling camp participant-related data. Provides methods to interact with camp participant data such as adding, retrieving, and editing information.
